						<p class="intro">
							A website's speed & performance matters more than ever. Most users now access the web over a mobile device and search engines such as Google and Bing now rank websites in search results primarily based on the websites speed. CodeCloud puts a strong focus on performance by compressing (minify) published files, using templates that have clean code with a focus on performance, and by using the fastest CDNs and databases in the world.
